channel.title: WIP Freeware Tune 2.1
channel.description:
WIP Freeware Tune 2.1 artist: tomasz.przetacznik@me.com genere: electronic
Link (recently updated) https://soundcloud.app.goo.gl/2sHy4KHBsL4259na7
This is actually a mix of 3 ideas/tracks, 1 up to 2.17 2 from to 2.17-7.10 3 form to ~7.10/7.11-end
About: This is still ongoing project, idea behind - to create complete 'mature' track with free version of Auxy, and those few basic instruments avalable in free mode. Actually limitations became opportunity to play with effects and options to gain better sounds, change this basic stuff so it would sound in acceptable manner. Enjoy!
Please remember to leave comments, here or directly at the Soundcloud!
Thanks to your feedback I can learn new things! & also check my other stuff! Regards Thomas
